name: White Paper Citizen DAO
description:
Mission
The mission of White Paper Citizens DAO is to stop the blockade and refuse to compel the whole people to nucleic acid.
Release the arrested protesters and allow the public to mourn the victims freely.
Freedom of the press, freedom of speech, freedom of association, and freedom to strike.
Compensation for the victims of the Urumqi fire and solidarity activists, erecting a memorial.
Help laid-off unemployed workers and students in need, and restore social production order.
Stop nucleic acid, anti-blockade, release compatriots, and be Freedom!
